Text.en:
Combat Feedback Vibrations<size:3>{
}<size:29>{
<b>{3D Haptics:} 3D Haptics are felt by all players in the environment, they can be triggered by the environment, enemies or players. 3D haptics of greater intensity are prioritised over lesser and intensity changes based on distance from each players position.<size:3>{
}
<b>{2D Haptics:} 2D Haptics are player specific. These are haptics reserved for player feedback such as large impacts, low health, channeling skills and UI navigation. They are generally higher priority than 3D haptics.}

Text.zh:
战斗反馈震动<size:3>{
}<size:29>{
<b><3D触觉反馈：> 3D触觉反馈可被环境中的所有玩家感知，可由环境、敌人或玩家触发。强度更高的3D触觉反馈会优先于强度较低的，且强度会根据距离每位玩家的位置而变化。<size:3>{
}
<b><2D触觉反馈：> 2D触觉反馈是玩家专属的。这些触觉反馈专为玩家反馈保留，例如重大冲击、生命过低、引导技能和界面导航。它们通常优先级高于3D触觉反馈。}

